text: 300px These fraternities are all members of the Cartellverband. The umbrella organizations are listed on a yellow background. Each fraternity is listed under its umbrella organization and is identified by a token consisting of the first letter of the umbrella organization and the membership number, based on the date of entry into the Cartellverband.
